29:54.709 --> 29:56.002
I think we
need to talk.

29:56.044 --> 29:57.128
Think I owe you
an apology.

29:57.170 --> 29:58.588
You do,
but that can wait.

29:58.630 --> 30:02.717
Right now, let's
do the damn thing.

30:02.759 --> 30:06.513
Monica: ♪ Now I see that
there ain't no us ♪

30:06.554 --> 30:09.224
♪ Baby, to me,
that's a definite plus ♪

30:09.265 --> 30:12.936
♪ If I can't get
you out of the streets ♪

30:12.977 --> 30:16.481
♪ Then you don't need
to be with me ♪

30:16.523 --> 30:20.610
[Applause and cheering]

30:29.035 --> 30:32.163
[Music playing]

30:32.205 --> 30:35.166
Marcus: Amara,
you look--wow.

30:35.208 --> 30:37.043
Right back at you.

30:41.214 --> 30:44.175
Why, thank you.
[Chuckles]

30:53.101 --> 30:54.936
[Pouring]

31:00.275 --> 31:04.779
All right.
To new beginnings.

31:07.740 --> 31:09.492
Mm.

31:11.494 --> 31:12.871
Look, Amara,

31:12.912 --> 31:15.123
I'm not asking
for a clean slate.

31:15.164 --> 31:17.750
I'm asking for
a chance to show you

31:17.792 --> 31:20.253
that I'm not the man
who disappears anymore.

31:20.295 --> 31:22.964
I'm the man who stays.

31:23.006 --> 31:24.299
[Dru Hill's "Beauty" playing]

31:24.340 --> 31:27.886
Ha ha. Marcus...

31:27.927 --> 31:29.846
Dru Hill? Ha ha!

31:29.888 --> 31:31.306
Ha ha ha!

31:31.347 --> 31:34.350
That was our song.
Boy, did you do this?

31:34.392 --> 31:36.936
That was me,
that was me.

31:39.439 --> 31:42.191
Ha ha ha ha!

31:46.905 --> 31:50.199
♪ Sorry,
didn't notice you there ♪

31:50.241 --> 31:54.287
♪ Then again,
you didn't notice me ♪

31:54.329 --> 31:58.291
♪ So we'll remain passersby ♪

31:58.333 --> 32:02.420
♪ Until the next time we speak ♪

32:02.462 --> 32:06.215
♪ I hope that I can
make you mine ♪

32:06.257 --> 32:11.471
♪ 'Fore another man
steals your heart... ♪

32:11.512 --> 32:13.681
You can't leave
before our dance.

32:13.723 --> 32:15.308
Who are you?

32:15.350 --> 32:17.143
It's more romantic
this way.

32:17.185 --> 32:19.312
[India Shawn's "Too Sweet"
playing]

32:21.689 --> 32:26.027
Shawn: ♪ You can't blame it
on the alcohol ♪

32:26.069 --> 32:30.281
♪ We both know
what you came here for ♪

32:30.323 --> 32:34.827
♪ You got me doin' rounds
'round your thoughts ♪

32:34.869 --> 32:38.748
♪ Tell me what you want,
oh, oh, oh ♪

32:38.790 --> 32:42.752
♪ You're good with your lips,
you feel right ♪

32:42.794 --> 32:46.756
♪ Your words took me places
at the right time ♪

32:46.798 --> 32:52.095
♪ Now you're cold 'cause
you ain't felt a soul so free ♪

32:52.136 --> 32:57.350
♪ Guess that's 'cause
you ain't met a woman like me ♪

32:57.392 --> 32:59.519
♪ Who love too sweet... ♪

32:59.560 --> 33:02.397
[Applause]

33:02.438 --> 33:04.023
Honey, if that
was our first dance,

33:04.065 --> 33:06.109
then I'm not ready...

33:06.150 --> 33:08.403
for the re--

33:08.444 --> 33:10.196
Shawn: ♪ I know that
you're weak, I see ♪

33:10.238 --> 33:13.741
♪ I'm too sweet,
