33:13.783 --> 33:17.787
♪ I'm too sweet,
that's why you can't reply ♪

33:17.829 --> 33:21.749
♪ I'm too sweet,
that's what you love 'bout me ♪

33:21.791 --> 33:26.087
♪ I know that you're weak,
I see ♪

33:26.129 --> 33:29.424
♪ It should be simple... ♪

33:29.465 --> 33:30.967
Charlotte and
the rest of your family

33:31.009 --> 33:32.677
finally got their way?

33:32.719 --> 33:37.015
Yeah, only because
I realized you were right.

33:37.056 --> 33:40.727
I was living in fear,
and I owe it to myself

33:40.768 --> 33:42.395
to see what I can make
of photography,

33:42.437 --> 33:45.314
so...I'm sorry.

33:45.356 --> 33:47.483
I owe you
an apology, too.

33:47.525 --> 33:50.278
I was using you to get
in good with Charlotte,

33:50.319 --> 33:52.655
and the more
she pressed me

33:52.697 --> 33:54.657
to think
about my future,

33:54.699 --> 33:56.492
the more
I ran from it.

33:56.534 --> 33:57.827
Why?

33:57.869 --> 33:59.370
My mom planned
my whole life,

33:59.412 --> 34:01.456
so nothing I ever
wanted mattered.

34:01.497 --> 34:03.541
Now that you have
the power to decide,

34:03.583 --> 34:05.585
you're scared you're gonna
make the wrong choices.

34:05.626 --> 34:07.170
Choosing Bringston
over Stanford

34:07.211 --> 34:09.255
was scary enough.

34:09.297 --> 34:12.675
I get that,
but the discovery
can be exciting.

34:12.717 --> 34:14.469
Ain't that what
college is all about,

34:14.510 --> 34:16.929
finding yourself?

34:16.971 --> 34:18.347
You know,
I actually liked

34:18.389 --> 34:20.558
learning something
new about you.

34:20.600 --> 34:22.310
-Yeah?
-Mm-hmm.

34:22.351 --> 34:25.354
Then you're gonna
love what comes next.

34:25.396 --> 34:26.481
[NOVO, Merezz & Tamer Hegab's
"Little Bit" playing]

34:26.522 --> 34:28.900
NOVO: ♪ No, no, no, no ♪

34:28.941 --> 34:30.443
I'm an incredible dancer.

34:30.485 --> 34:31.778
-Oh, really?
-Mm-hmm.

34:31.819 --> 34:33.821
NOVO: ♪ No, no, no, no ♪

34:33.863 --> 34:35.698
We'll see
about that.

34:35.740 --> 34:38.242
NOVO: ♪ Understand, understand ♪

34:38.284 --> 34:40.745
♪ There ain't nothing
you can do about it ♪

34:40.787 --> 34:43.498
♪ Flip my main, that's my way ♪

34:43.539 --> 34:45.374
♪ There ain't nothing
you can do about it ♪

34:45.416 --> 34:48.169
♪ That's the way
I've been played ♪

34:48.211 --> 34:50.713
♪ Like you brought it
out of me ♪

34:50.755 --> 34:53.049
♪ Spend my time drinking far ♪

34:53.091 --> 34:54.675
♪ When it's bright,
I'm out to see... ♪

34:54.717 --> 34:57.136
J.R.: Damon.

34:57.178 --> 34:59.722
Man, I'm sorry.

34:59.764 --> 35:01.390
You told me how you
felt about Simone.

35:01.432 --> 35:02.892
I should've
supported you,

35:02.934 --> 35:04.644
not discouraged you.

35:07.021 --> 35:09.816
I appreciate that,
man, for real.

35:11.067 --> 35:13.277
So what changed
your mind?

35:13.319 --> 35:15.404
Heh! Gabby. Heh.

35:15.446 --> 35:16.906
What changed your mind

35:16.948 --> 35:18.825
about coming to
the masquerade ball?

35:18.866 --> 35:21.953
Oddly...Cam.

35:21.994 --> 35:24.372
Ha! I'm gonna need
that story later.

35:24.413 --> 35:26.666
Yeah. I came
to talk to Simone,

35:26.707 --> 35:29.961
and I had my moment,
bro, but...

35:31.838 --> 35:33.297
just couldn't
go through with it.

35:33.339 --> 35:34.674
I don't know why.

35:34.715 --> 35:35.967
You were afraid
that if she

35:36.008 --> 35:37.510
didn't return
your feelings,

35:37.552 --> 35:39.303
you'll lose one
of your best friends.

35:39.345 --> 35:40.596
Yeah, and you put
that in my head.

35:40.638 --> 35:42.098
And I was wrong
because truth is,

35:42.140 --> 35:43.808
you and Simone have
never been just friends,

35:43.850 --> 35:45.518
not since the first day
on the quad.

35:45.560 --> 35:48.062
Your feelings have been
so much more than that.

35:48.104 --> 35:49.730
Guess at this point,

35:49.772 --> 35:52.358
I ain't got
nothing to lose.

35:52.400 --> 35:54.360
And everything to gain,
and she might just
return your feelings.

35:54.402 --> 35:56.070
I won't know until
I put it out there.

35:56.112 --> 35:58.489
Listen, that's the only way
you'll be able to move on,

35:58.531 --> 36:02.243
and no matter what happens,
I'll be here to listen.

36:02.285 --> 36:04.203
[Both chuckle]

36:09.167 --> 36:10.835
So are we gonna talk,

36:10.877 --> 36:14.005
or are we just gonna dance
until our feet fall off?

36:14.046 --> 36:15.631
Sure. You can start
by telling me

36:15.673 --> 36:18.384
why you sonned me
in front of everyone.

36:18.426 --> 36:20.386
I really needed you
this weekend,

36:20.428 --> 36:22.555
and then suddenly,
it felt like all your
new friends came first.

36:22.597 --> 36:24.140
That's not even
a little true.

36:24.182 --> 36:26.350
I always show up
for you, Kee, always.

36:26.392 --> 36:28.186
I know,
but for an organization

36:28.227 --> 36:29.687
you joined just
for scholarships,

36:29.729 --> 36:31.189
you spend
a lot of time with them.

36:31.230 --> 36:32.732
Yeah, sure.

36:32.773 --> 36:34.650
I originally joined
KEK for the money,

36:34.692 --> 36:36.652
but I found something
I didn't think I'd find

36:36.694 --> 36:39.280
after football--
a brotherhood.

36:39.322 --> 36:41.240
KEK gave that back
to me,

36:41.282 --> 36:42.825
and I'm not
gonna apologize

36:42.867 --> 36:45.369
for wanting that
for myself.

36:45.411 --> 36:49.207
And you shouldn't
have to.

36:49.248 --> 36:52.543
I'm really
happy for you.

36:52.585 --> 36:54.629
Dr. Pace really
got me in my head.

36:54.670 --> 36:56.422
Man, if I never hear
that woman's name again,

36:56.464 --> 36:58.257
it'll be too soon.

36:58.299 --> 36:59.717
What'd she do now?

36:59.759 --> 37:01.093
She said she's
gonna flunk me

37:01.135 --> 37:02.511
because students
can't take paid gigs.

37:02.553 --> 37:04.472
For real?
Can she even do that?

37:04.513 --> 37:06.849
I don't know. Apparently, she
can do whatever she wants.

37:06.891 --> 37:09.143
Nah. My girl is
way too good
to go out like that.

37:09.185 --> 37:12.146
Come on. We're
gonna find a way
out of this, OK?

37:12.188 --> 37:15.358
♪ It never gets easier... ♪

37:20.488 --> 37:22.698
Simone: Um, Charlotte,

37:22.740 --> 37:25.117
can I talk to you
for a second?

37:25.159 --> 37:27.453
I love tennis.

37:27.495 --> 37:29.497
I believe
it's my future,

37:29.538 --> 37:31.165
but I'm really
excited to see

37:31.207 --> 37:33.042
what else is
out there for me,

37:33.084 --> 37:34.543
and I'd love it
if you were there

37:34.585 --> 37:36.212
guiding me
along the way.

37:36.254 --> 37:38.506
I love everything about
what you just said,

37:38.547 --> 37:40.091
and once you cross,
you'll not only have

37:40.132 --> 37:43.094
a big sister
but a mentor for life.

37:43.135 --> 37:44.845
Period.

37:44.887 --> 37:47.473
I'll e-mail you my top 5
summer internship options,

37:47.515 --> 37:49.475
and we can talk
about them next week?

37:49.517 --> 37:52.019
Absolutely.
I'll be in touch.

37:52.061 --> 37:54.647
And whatever you
said to Orlando,

37:54.689 --> 37:56.190
I've never
seen him so happy

37:56.232 --> 37:57.650
to pick up a camera.

37:57.692 --> 37:59.360
Thank you.

38:10.162 --> 38:12.456
So what
could possibly have

38:12.498 --> 38:14.083
the most beautiful
girl in the room

38:14.125 --> 38:16.752
looking so sad?

38:16.794 --> 38:19.297
I'm not sad,
just deep in thought.

38:19.338 --> 38:21.424
Well, if you're willing,
I have a bag full of pennies

38:21.465 --> 38:24.135
for even
just one thought.

38:24.176 --> 38:25.845
OK.

38:25.886 --> 38:29.849
Um, I took a chance

38:29.890 --> 38:32.435
and fought
for love tonight.

38:32.476 --> 38:35.229
It didn't
go well, but--

38:35.271 --> 38:37.023
Sorry to hear that.

38:37.064 --> 38:39.650
It's OK, you know?
I took a shot,

38:39.692 --> 38:43.362
and now I have the
closure I need...

38:43.404 --> 38:46.407
and, um,
as for tennis,

38:46.449 --> 38:48.617
I'm gonna sign up
for a Challenger Match,

38:48.659 --> 38:51.620
and if it goes well,
I'm going pro.

38:51.662 --> 38:53.331
Well, I guess there's
only one thing left

38:53.372 --> 38:55.207
to do from here.

38:55.249 --> 38:56.876
What?

38:56.917 --> 39:01.714
Dance with me.
Just one dance, Thea.

39:01.756 --> 39:03.007
-OK.
-Yeah?

39:03.049 --> 39:05.468
Fine. Ha ha!

39:07.887 --> 39:09.764
Hi, Dr. Pace.

39:11.891 --> 39:13.517
So...

39:15.436 --> 39:17.021
I just wanted
to let you know,

39:17.063 --> 39:18.564
I had the
Masquerade Committee

39:18.606 --> 39:20.941
donate my choreography
fee to charity.

39:20.983 --> 39:25.446
That's very kind,
Ms. McCalla,

39:25.488 --> 39:28.240
but I'm afraid
that's a technicality.

39:28.282 --> 39:29.658
You still
accepted payment.

39:29.700 --> 39:31.202
Well, technically,
no, I didn't.

39:31.243 --> 39:32.495
I never touched it.

39:32.536 --> 39:34.538
They donated it,
not me,

39:34.580 --> 39:36.123
so unless you
have something else

39:36.165 --> 39:38.584
you want
to fail me for...

39:38.626 --> 39:41.170
Guess I'll see you
in class, then.

39:41.212 --> 39:43.255
I guess so.

39:49.762 --> 39:52.890
That was a night
I won't soon forget.

39:52.932 --> 39:54.767
Yeah.

39:54.809 --> 39:57.353
Well, good things come
to those who wait.

39:57.395 --> 40:00.272
I guess so.

40:05.820 --> 40:07.780
Good night, Amara.

40:11.867 --> 40:14.328
Who says the night
has to end?

40:26.465 --> 40:29.802
♪ Oh, like a rocket
through the white ♪

40:29.844 --> 40:31.637
♪ Ripped from a feeling ♪

40:31.679 --> 40:33.848
♪ All right, all right ♪

40:36.559 --> 40:39.854
♪ Tonight what I
don't want to do is numb ♪

40:39.895 --> 40:41.730
♪ 'Cause I can't
really feel it ♪

40:41.772 --> 40:44.233
♪ Oh, my, oh, my ♪

40:44.275 --> 40:46.735
[Cell phone vibrates and chimes]

40:46.777 --> 40:49.655
♪ When the sky starts
turning black ♪

40:49.697 --> 40:52.324
♪ Don't get lost in that ♪

40:52.366 --> 40:55.411
♪ The dark
won't last forever... ♪

40:56.745 --> 40:58.581
Well, Samuel...

40:58.622 --> 41:00.499
[Chuckles]

41:00.541 --> 41:02.835
I didn't think
I was gonna see you
again tonight.

41:02.877 --> 41:05.713
Actually, um, heh!

41:05.754 --> 41:10.009
Damon was hoping that
he could talk to Simone,

41:10.050 --> 41:11.635
if you didn't mind.

41:11.677 --> 41:14.305
Oh, God.

41:14.346 --> 41:16.182
Why do I get the feeling
you're gonna say

41:16.223 --> 41:17.892
we can't go back
to being friends?

41:17.933 --> 41:20.352
I haven't been
completely honest

41:20.394 --> 41:23.939
about my feelings.

41:23.981 --> 41:26.066
Truth is, I love you.

41:26.108 --> 41:27.568
I've always loved you.

41:27.610 --> 41:29.153
I loved you since
I stole your phone

41:29.195 --> 41:32.114
at homecoming
two years ago.

41:32.156 --> 41:33.741
I want more, Simone,

41:33.782 --> 41:38.078
but if you don't,
I'll respect that.

41:38.120 --> 41:40.581
Choice is yours.

41:42.500 --> 41:44.418
♪ Ooh, ooh, wait ♪

41:44.460 --> 41:47.129
♪ Ooh, ooh, wait ♪

41:47.171 --> 41:52.218
♪ Ooh, ohh, till the stars
come back to us ♪

42:19.745 --> 42:21.163
Greg,
move your head.
